


Devops is the evolution of mehodoligis for the purpose of bringing development and operation together. 
Find tools that improve collaboration, less context switching, automation and more oersavalbity. 
Two approaches: 
	All in one : integrate with other third-party tools
	open toolchain : can be customized for a team’s needs with different tools. 


Regardless of toolchain choice: Use the right tools to address the key phases of the DevOps lifecycle:
										Plan
										Build
										Continuous integration and deployment 
										Monitor 
										Operate	
										Continuous feedback  
